main: ^A waterfall of the Agus River in the Northern Mindanao region of the Philippines. It is sometimes called the "twin falls" as the flow is separated by a rock at the brink of the waterfall.

c-0: ^It is also the primary source of electric power for Iligan City popularly known as the “City of Majestic Waterfalls” and it is the second highest waterfalls in the Philippines.
